---
layout: default
---
<article>
    <div id="about" class="section">
        <div class="t-container">
            {% include 'avatar.njk' %}
            <p>Nice to meet you <span class="emoji" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ‘‹</span>. Iâ€™m a <mark title="Product Design, Interaction Design, User Experience & User Interface Design">multidisciplinary designer</mark> currently based in {{ site.location }}.</p>
            <p>My work focuses on building thoughtful, intuitive, and delightful digital products with a devotion to the quality, design process, transparency, and sharing what I learn.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="works" class="section">
        <div class="t-container">
            <h2>Latest works</h2>
        </div>
        <ol>
            {% for work in collections.work %}
                <li class="work{% if work.url != false %} work--reels{% endif %}">
                    {% if work.url == false %}
                        <img src="{{ '/static/' + work.fileSlug + '.jpg' | url }}" srcset="{{ '/static/' + work.fileSlug + '@1.5x.jpg' | url }} 1.5x, {{ '/static/' + work.fileSlug + '@2x.jpg' | url }} 2x" alt="{{ work.data.title }}{% if work.data.client %} â€“ {{ work.data.client }}{% endif %}" loading="lazy">
                    {% else %}
                        <a class="work-link t-hover--2" href="{{ work.url | url }}" rel="bookmark" target="_parent" title="{{ work.data.title }}{% if work.data.client %} â€“ {{ work.data.client }}{% endif %}">
                            <span class="link-label">Case study</span>
                            <img src="{{ '/static/' + work.fileSlug + '.jpg' | url }}" srcset="{{ '/static/' + work.fileSlug + '@1.5x.jpg' | url }} 1.5x, {{ '/static/' + work.fileSlug + '@2x.jpg' | url }} 2x" alt="{{ work.data.title }}{% if work.data.client %} â€“ {{ work.data.client }}{% endif %}" loading="lazy">
                        </a>
                    {% endif %}
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ol>
    </div>
    {% if skills %}
        <div id="expertises" class="section">
            <div class="t-container">
                <h2>Expertises</h2>
                <ul class="t-list-horizontal">
                    {% for expertise in skills %}
                        <li class="t-list-horizontal--item t-list-horizontal--item--distance-1">
                            {{ expertise }}
                            <img src="{{ '/static/' + expertise | normalize + '.svg' }}" alt="{{ expertise }}" loading="lazy">
                        </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    {% endif %}
    <div id="contact" class="section">
        <div class="t-container">
            <h2>Experience</h2>
            <p>Over the last {% experience %} years, I had the privilege to improve products used and loved by many users, these are some of the clients:</p>
            {% if clients %}
                <ol class="t-list-horizontal">
                    {% for client in clients %}
                        <li class="t-list-horizontal--item t-list-horizontal--item--distance-2">
                            {% if client.url %}
                                <a href="{{ client.url | url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank" title="{{ client.title }}">
                                    {% include client.title | slug + '.svg' %}
                                </a>
                            {% else %}
                                {% include client.title | slug + '.svg' %}
                            {% endif %}
                        </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ol>
            {% endif %}
            <p>If youâ€™d like me to work on your product/service or just say hello, please feel free to reach me via email.</p>
            <a class="button t-hover--1" href="mailto:{{ site.mail }}" title="Contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</article>